Package: mupdog
Title: Extension of the updog Method for Genotyping Autopolyploids
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("David", "Gerard", email = "dcgerard@uchicago.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package accounts for correlation between individuals' genotypes
	     in the genotyping procedure by wielding information across all SNPs.
	     This requires using a variational approximation.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
